data.description: This delightful home features a single story layout with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, spanning over 1,629 sq ft. Conveniently situated near schools, shopping centers, parks, and more, it offers a well-equipped kitchen with granite countertops and ample cabinet space. Adjacent to the dining room, a sunroom provides additional seating or can be used as an office. The master suite boasts a spacious walk-in closet and an ensuite with a vanity area. Two additional bedrooms offer generous storage with large closets. Recently updated with leased solar panels and water-friendly landscaping in the front yard, this home is both eco-friendly and low-maintenance. Don't miss out on the opportunity to view this home, as it won't be available for long!
